Author: scribble-stars
Text: i weirdly do this all the time too? my siblings will eat something that was supposed to be for me, or my favorite cereal, and i’ll just start hoarding different foods in my room. another weird thing i do is with my school lunches. when i pack myself and my siblings lunch in the morning, i purposefully give myself the best things, even though i just give my lunch to whoever asks for it in my friend group that day. i always feel guilty about it, but i know where you’re coming from
